1. Make sure the version will be right (for a new minor version that means that
   you should set the patch level to -1 so dcvs will bump it to 0)

2. Write ChangeLog entry.

3. Update PROJECT_NUMBER in Doxyfile.

4. make dist, check that it builds and installs correctly.

5. CVS commit.

6. cvs tag Release_X_Y_Z

7. Sign (gpg -b) and upload dist tarball 
   (sftp larsl@dl.sv.nongnu.org:/releases/ll-plugins).

8. Generate new API documentation, upload it, update the redirect page.

9. Update webpages.

10. Announce on http://freshmeat.net and any relevant mailing lists.
